Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,厅中的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}苏宁{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}玉她神色如常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}从她眼中读出了一丝凄苦
